It's a pocket reference for grep.

Seriously, do a search for grep.

From Wikipedia:

grep is a command line text search utility originally written for Unix.

GREP - Global Regular Expression Print is a utility (command) in Unix like operating systems. It is a very handy tool for Unix OS like Admins and Users.

A good book to share with all of you :)
